author: alexdma
msg: - Removed OntologyIndex and its implementation from OntoNet, as they are no longer needed due to OntologyProvider managing stored ontologies. (STANBOL-332)
- SessionManager implementation is now an independent OSGi service component and can no longer be accessed by the ONManager. All uses have been refactored accordingly. (STANBOL-247)
- Early support for configurable session limits. (STANBOL-247)
- Reengineers were not using sessions earlier, so references to SessionManager were removed. (STANBOL-247)
